            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/3226">Castracane</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3214">Ubertelli</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/3210"
                            key="#Fisheries #Mills #Seigneurial_district">Puteo</placeName>, iam
                        dato consenso a patre suo, concessit et prodonavit atque promisit
                                <persName><name ref="Montanus">Montaninus</name></persName> (sic)
                        rectori de <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">ospitali</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Teupasci</placeName></orgName> omnes terras, casas et res et omines,
                        casinas et aquas (et sepes cum omni hedificio et pertinentia sua) et silvas,
                        paxsturis et omnibus rebus illis quas predictum hospitale habet in <rs
                            key="#Seigneurial_district">curia de Puteo</rs> vel in eius finibus et
                        ei pertinet sive ex parte quondam <persName ref="#people/3215"
                            >Passavantis</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3216"
                            >Sesmondi</persName> sive per acquistum aut alio quocumque modo. Et
                        promisit omnes suprascriptas res suprascripto hospitali adiuvare et
                        defendere. Et fuit similiter pactum et conventum predicto Montanino pro
                        suprascripto hospitali hedificare cum eo <rs key="#Mills">molendinum</rs> in
                        aqua de <rs key="#Rivers">Giusciana</rs>, ad comunes expensas, per
                        medietatem que comuni accordamento deinceps faciende erunt. Et a prato <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> usque ad molinum de <placeName key="#Mills"
                            ref="#places/3244">Furnole</placeName> non debet aliquo tempore ipse vel
                        eius heredes aliquod molinum facere, nec debent aliquod hedificium facere
                        quod suprascripto molino deberat nocere. Et quicquid habuerint pro ipso
                        molino vel pro <rs key="#Fisheries">piscaria</rs> que ibi erit debet esse
                        comune per medium inter eos. Et viam ad eundum et redeundum debet habere
                        suprascriptum molinum, et predictus Castracane concedere eam et non
                        contedere aliquo modo, nec debet Castracane contrariare terram vel scopas
                        que ad predictam sepem conciandam necesse fuerint. Immo, debet eas concedere
                        suprascripto hospitali. Unde suprascriptus Montaninus, pro suprascripto
                        hospitali, dedit meritum predicto Castracani et patri eius suam portionem
                        que est <rs key="#Meritum/launechild">medietas de mascio</rs> de
                                <persName><name ref="Riccius da Petriolo">Riccio</name> da
                                <placeName ref="#places/284">Petriolo</placeName></persName>, eo
                        pacto et ea conditione quod, si suprascriptus Castracane (vel eius filii)
                        mortuus fuerit sine heredes de legittima uxore, quod ea medietas revertatur
                        ad hospitale. Vel si non fuerint suprascripta pacta et conventa omnia
                        suprascripto hospitali observata, et que in hanc cartulam continentur quod
                        similiter revertatur ad hospitale cum pena mille sol. lucensis monete. Nec
                        debet vendere vel pignorare aut alienare suprascriptum mascium vel vendere
                        aut (pignorare) suprascriptum molinum (vel pescariam) nisi suprascripto
                        hospitali. Hec omnia debent observare suprascripto hospitali per bonam fidem
                        sine fraude. Actum in suprascripto hospitale, presentia <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Widoloctus">Guidolotti</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Alferius">Alfieri</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Heinricus">Henrici</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Ildebertus">Ildeberti</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bonushomulus">Bonsomi</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Betto">Betti</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Hubertellus">Ubertelli</name></persName> de
                        (â€¦), <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Boianus">Boiani</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Martinaccius">Martinacci</name></persName>. Ego
                            <persName key="#Causidicus #Witness #Writer"><name ref="Rodelandus"
                                >Rolandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs> rogatus testis interfui, M C
                        sexagesimo quarto, IIII idus martii, ind. XIII.</ab>
